790,IssueCommentEvent,2018-01-30 19:52:44+00:00,30492678,facetoe/zenpy,13722050,bjaus,,,292606753,361713859,"I ended up taking the following approach:
```python
for ticket in zd_client.search(type='ticket', created_between=([start_date], [end_date])):
    for audit in zd_client.tickets.audits(ticket.id):
        for event in audit.events:
            for attachment in event.get('attachments', []):
                res = request.get(attachment['content_url'], auth=('user', 'password'))
                with open(attachment['file_name'], 'wb') as fout:
                    fout.write(res._content)
```
Which might not be the best approach but it did the trick. Thanks for making this wrapper straight forward. Solid work!",{},NONE,User,False
