3106,IssueCommentEvent,2017-02-08 14:11:18+00:00,59235,mkleehammer/pyodbc,2080150,iagomez,,,205932837,278338638,"@keitherskine So even though the DSN's are not listed in the output, I can still connect to them, but the code fails as shown below

