3337,IssueCommentEvent,2018-05-17 04:59:53+00:00,4209988,SethMMorton/natsort,1596189,SethMMorton,,,323870806,389744936,"This was done intentionally by introducing the new `src` folder - see https://blog.ionelmc.ro/2014/05/25/python-packaging/ for the motivation for making this change. The main point is that testing against a non-installed version does not guarantee that one is testing against what gets installed.

In https://github.com/SethMMorton/natsort#how-to-run-tests I note that using [tox](https://tox.readthedocs.io/en/latest/) or [pipenv](https://github.com/pypa/pipenv) can be used to allow you to test the freshly built version as in a virtual environment.

Will this a hardship for you?",{},OWNER,User,False
