4838,IssueCommentEvent,2015-11-13 00:47:32+00:00,8582627,mgedmin/check-manifest,210587,mauritsvanrees,,,115521992,156282584,"AFAIK really empty directories never end up in git and never and up in an sdist. But in some cases you do want a directory in there, so adding a hidden file makes sense, as long as that file itself is then included in the sdist via the manifest. So I think check-manifest is right in complaining.

