5099,IssueCommentEvent,2015-06-12 07:56:58+00:00,9376661,lorenzofox3/Smart-Table,9194223,AndrewIsh,,,86232721,111399033,"Thanks for the suggestion @lorenzofox3. I think I will have to resort to returning a promise. It feels like it shouldn't be necessary, binding to the TagService.allTags object should be sufficient, I've certainly never had any problems with controllers not seeing changes in service objects before.

