5260,IssueCommentEvent,2018-04-08 06:24:22+00:00,127026864,Prodicode/ann-visualizer,32748771,Prodicode,,,312273438,379524322,"I notice that you are passing a Model object to the `ann_viz()` function. You can try passing an Sequential object.

Look at the example in Readme where it visualizez a simple Dense Neural Network, and build your model using the `Sequential().add()` function. Here's an example:

```python
model = Sequential()
model.add(Dense(80, input_shape=(4,), activation='sigmoid'));

#etc
#Add your other layers
#Compile NN
``` ",{},OWNER,User,False
