5759,IssueCommentEvent,2015-06-01 14:18:11+00:00,4607655,spookylukey/django-paypal,440051,thiagogds,,,33307251,107511681,"I'm having the same issue.
I looked it up and in fact it is two problems :pensive: 

1st: **UnicodeDecodeError**
