6842,IssueCommentEvent,2018-06-14 09:03:40+00:00,34864402,apache/incubator-mxnet,22143873,wyz2016,47359,apache,163068986,397224933,"I re-git mxnet.git and used --recursive , but it doesn't works. Then, I find an answer:
link: https://stackoverflow.com/posts/48272520/edit, and it works for me.
```
