8036,IssueCommentEvent,2017-07-31 22:35:55+00:00,6670942,boto/botocore,1935727,joguSD,327752,boto,244209269,319216014,"There actually already is a unit test for this exact situation. It can be seen [here](https://github.com/boto/botocore/blob/develop/tests/unit/test_paginate.py#L722). However, a unit test is insufficient to catch this as it's not an issue with the pagination or validation code independently but both of them combined, hence the functional test. ",{},,User,False
