8265,IssueCommentEvent,2016-05-25 13:53:36+00:00,1126087,gitpython-developers/GitPython,9481784,josefsachsconning,503709,gitpython-developers,156691945,221583041,"Thanks for trying.  In case it helps anyone, `fetch_info_lines` is
