8825,IssueCommentEvent,2018-05-25 17:19:45+00:00,633141,pusher/pusher-http-python,5316211,EsauPR,739550,pusher,19215792,392124792,"Cause the number of messages are too many (300 messages per minute) within a very short time we use the trigger_batch method. The error is raised around every hour although the last logs show a long time between each error.

