9041,IssueCommentEvent,2018-06-06 09:04:00+00:00,2014929,scikit-image/scikit-image,492549,jni,897180,scikit-image,294159499,394998463,"Cool! Well, it seems a lot cleaner than comparable Cython, and for this one benchmark at least, performance is identical:

