10978,IssueCommentEvent,2016-01-21 12:45:42+00:00,16316451,GoogleCloudPlatform/gcloud-python,879743,andrazhribernik,2810941,GoogleCloudPlatform,127884936,173559647,"Sorry for not adding any description and tests. It is basically a bug fix.

When we tried to use this functionality:

    from gcloud import pubsub
    client = pubsub.Client(project=<project_name>)
