    133 

/Users/andrazhribernik/cytora/gcloud-python/gcloud/pubsub/subscription.pyc in from_api_repr(cls, resource, client, topics)
     71             # NOTE: This duplicates behavior from Topic.from_api_repr to avoid
     72             #       an import cycle.
