10998,IssueCommentEvent,2015-06-18 03:56:21+00:00,24478149,GoogleCloudPlatform/appengine-pipelines,419831,NickFranceschina,2810941,GoogleCloudPlatform,89089853,113027919,"Funny... that's pretty much _exactly_ our pipeline subclass paradigm as well

