11612,IssueCommentEvent,2015-06-06 21:55:02+00:00,7695747,wal-e/wal-e,768067,diranged,3310438,wal-e,28526091,109653426,"@fdr, fyi we just ran into this problem again twice in a row using WAL-E 0.8.0. We hadn't seen it in a long time, so we're still unsure of how it happens. Just an FYI, here's the stack trace:

```++ dirname /mnt/postgres-scripts/wale/wale_restore_command.sh
+ MYPATH=/mnt/postgres-scripts/wale
