```

 for f in element.files:
            p_table = self.document.tables[-1].rows[2].cells[1].add_paragraph()
            file_name = f.split('/')[-1]
            file_path = 'EVIDENCES/{}'.format(file_name)  
            # ajout du lien
            add_hyperlink(p_table,file_name, file_path)
```

this worked just fine for me
