11687,IssueCommentEvent,2016-12-12 10:16:30+00:00,9861437,imageio/imageio,3015475,almarklein,3678179,imageio,194860709,266390867,"The main purpose of `generate_candidate_libs()` is to be able to detect libs (like FreeImage) by looking in all the common places. Regardless of what was found, `load_lib()` will always first use `ctypes.cdll.LoadLibrary` with the lib name (not path) to let ctypes resolve it.",{},,User,False
