12291,IssueCommentEvent,2016-06-19 10:56:32+00:00,3791384,coursera-dl/coursera-dl,340676,balta2ar,5588942,coursera-dl,161066931,226991054,"There are numerous ways to workaround it in Linux:

```
# Use backticks
coursera-dl -n ~/.netrc --resume --video-resolution 720p -sl en -pl `cat ../cs3.csv`

# Use xargs
cat ../cs3.csv | xargs coursera-dl -n ~/.netrc --resume --video-resolution 720p -sl en -pl

# Use while read
cat ../cs3.csv | while read course; do
    coursera-dl -n ~/.netrc --resume --video-resolution 720p -sl en -pl $course
done
```

",{},,User,False
