12830,IssueCommentEvent,2016-06-22 00:52:02+00:00,6235174,conda/conda,2797735,mcg1969,6392739,conda,161553524,227614454,"The conda channel specification is actually well-tuned to be served from an entirely static location. Any dynamic generation we're doing is unnecessary from conda's perspective, although I certainly concede there may be useful reasons to intervene in some sort of dynamic fashion (e.g., analytics collection)",{},,User,False
