13157,IssueCommentEvent,2016-10-17 20:46:45+00:00,51040886,Azure/azure-cli,5723682,tjprescott,6844498,Azure,183168610,254328820,"@derekbekoe this may be an issue then. In the generic update, 'this_tag' and 'thisTag' are both valid. The generic update logic is such that it will not convert the case for you, but one problem could be that if you show something and that output logic converts the case for you, and you then try to update that, you could get bizarre behavior:

