13712,IssueCommentEvent,2017-05-03 13:10:33+00:00,33653601,jupyter/notebook,151929,minrk,7388996,jupyter,224083693,298905979,"The only differences I see between that and a [known-working configuration](https://github.com/jupyterhub/jupyterhub-deploy-teaching/blob/master/roles/nginx/templates/nginx.conf.j2#L76) are:

1. `proxy_set_header Upgrade` uses `$http_upgrade` not `""websocket""`
