16166,IssueCommentEvent,2015-10-22 15:03:29+00:00,43852872,PulpQE/pulp-smash,1028657,asmacdo,14839747,PulpQE,112683231,150254584,"### Basic ""it works"":

GET:
`http --json -a admin:admin --verify=no GET 'https://localhost/pulp/api/v2/repositories/search/?filters={}`
POST:
`http --json -a admin:admin --verify=no POST 'https://localhost/pulp/api/v2/repositories/search/' criteria:='{""filters"": {}}'`


###  Basic search by id:

GET:
`http --json -a admin:admin --verify=no GET 'https://localhost/pulp/api/v2/repositories/search/?filters={""id"":""zoo""}'`

POST:
`http --json -a admin:admin --verify=no POST 'https://localhost/pulp/api/v2/repositories/search/' criteria:='{""filters"": {""id"": ""zoo""}}'`


### Test that ""options"" arguments work:

GET:
`http --json -a admin:admin --verify=no GET 'https://localhost/pulp/api/v2/repositories/search/?filters={""id"": ""zoo""}&details=true'`

POST:
`http --json -a admin:admin --verify=no POST 'https://localhost/pulp/api/v2/repositories/search/' criteria:='{""filters"": {""id"": ""zoo""}}' details=true`


### Test that field/fields work:

GET:
`http --json -a admin:admin --verify=no POST 'https://localhost/pulp/api/v2/repositories/search/' criteria:='{""filters"": {""id"": ""zoo""}}' details=true`

POST:
`http --json -a admin:admin --verify=no GET 'https://localhost/pulp/api/v2/repositories/search/?filters={""id"": ""zoo""}&field=id'`


### Test limit:

GET:
`http --json -a admin:admin --verify=no GET 'https://localhost/pulp/api/v2/repositories/search/?filters={}&limit=1'`

POST:
`http --json -a admin:admin --verify=no POST 'https://localhost/pulp/api/v2/repositories/search/' criteria:='{""filters"": {}, ""limit"": 1}'`


### Test Sort:

GET:
`http --json -a admin:admin --verify=no GET 'https://localhost/pulp/api/v2/repositories/search/?filters={}&sort=[[""id"", ""ascending""]]'`

POST:
`http --json -a admin:admin --verify=no POST 'https://localhost/pulp/api/v2/repositories/search/' criteria:='{""filters"": {}, ""sort"": [[""id"", ""descending""]]}'`


### Skip:

GET:
`http --json -a admin:admin --verify=no GET 'https://localhost/pulp/api/v2/repositories/search/?filters={}&sort=[[""id"", ""ascending""]]&skip=1'`

POST:
`http --json -a admin:admin --verify=no POST 'https://localhost/pulp/api/v2/repositories/search/' criteria:='{""filters"": {}, ""sort"": [[""id"", ""descending""]], ""skip"": ""1""}'`",{},,User,False
