17148,IssueCommentEvent,2018-04-03 01:36:52+00:00,26516210,certbot/certbot,1813285,sydneyli,17889013,certbot,286077126,378100191,"@TheNavigat So, there's a lot of not-nice things about the nginx parser and it would be unfortunate if the Dovecot plugin inherited all of those problems. @ohemorange and I will probably be refactoring the nginx parsing code soon, so we can get rid of UnspacedList (which I noticed you are using in #5751).

