17234,IssueCommentEvent,2017-08-31 01:02:16+00:00,58499929,pylti/lti,425099,ryanhiebert,19295652,pylti,253932365,326159870,"The documentation is exactly as you've described it: sparse. This is something that I would love to see a pull request for, but I haven't had the time to get around to it yet.

