18090,IssueCommentEvent,2018-01-16 02:23:10+00:00,35531022,opendatacube/datacube-core,1428024,Kirill888,26125288,opendatacube,287323027,357835189,"Problem is not specific to GeoTiff, rather point load is broken whenever output crs differs from native. It's just that with scene products you must specify CRS since there is no global product CRS and so you are more likely to hit this problem.

Load should probably detect point queries and rather than re-projecting a `1x1` raster into a different coordinate frame, instead should transform query point to the native projection of the source file and read that coordinate without re-projection.",{},CONTRIBUTOR,User,False
