18350,IssueCommentEvent,2018-04-20 10:19:06+00:00,60626727,tensorlayer/tensorlayer,10923599,DEKHTIARJonathan,32261543,tensorlayer,316087929,383053167,"Here is some code to help on the implementation, the ""Layer"" class needs to be made **subscriptable**.

